content: Works great! It would be nice if it also supported 850 Hz shift.
I like this app cause it does what it says It works.... I purchased some more of your apps because They Work great!! I thank u very much and keep up the very good work.

Like all Wolphi apps, this one works perfectly. I use it to decode ITTY feeds and it never fails to demodulate all of the text. A fantastic tool. I own several other apps made by Wolphi LLC and they all perform flawlessly.  Thank you for making outstanding products for the amateur radio community.
If it would send what I paste to the clipboard, that would be great. Not a lot of use to me presently.

I had previously purchased this and it seems it was deleted from the app 
shop and then readded again. Other than that I have purchased all of 
Wolphi's apps.

Great app. My only wish, as others have mentioned, is for additional baud / 
shift options.
Good app. But I don't transmit so all the macro/tx buttons are pointless to me, whereas the baud, shift etc options are needlessly hidden behind the menu, making it a little extra work to use.

Best App out their for this mode. Been using it for a few years now. Just reinstalled on a replacement android tablet.   It provides everything for the ham radio mode.  Decodes  the websdr beautifully. Open websdr via Firefox find a signal ,then open droid rtty and you will find a panoramic display of signals, same applies to droid psk. So multitasking for RX works well.
This app is great just put your phone close to the radio speaker and it starts to decode the rtty data.....
...on my samsung galaxy mega 2 with android 4.4.4.
Works great, just wish it auto locked on stations like droid psk

It just works, what more can I say. It always amazes me what it can pull out of the noise.  Communications with author yield quick responses with helpful instructions.   I plan to purchase more apps from Wolphi LLC.

It would be great to have more choices of frequency shift and baud rates in order to copy some of the 'numbers' stations. Also, it seems to be draining power by using GPS on my phone even when the the app has exited!

Excellent piece of software, ideal for portable operation as well as fixed station. Very easy to set up and use. I have used it in contests to great effect. I would highly recommend this to anyone , beginner or old hands at digital modes. Give it a try it's great fun especially when propagation is poor. Also try DroidPSK for PSK31 and 63, same layout and set up as DroidRTTY making these two great companion programs. Customer support also excellent very fast replies to queries though I doubt you'll have many as it's all set out so straight forward . Now go get it ! you won't regret it  Frank G4HBI
